comments.body: does this change match ones in later react-dom versions?

#34031 made dependent changes to `types/react-dom/v15/react-dom-tests.ts` (older) and `types/react-dom/test-utils/index.d.ts` (latest). 197675585a2fd685b831e8f2c74036eedd96a020 propagates the change to the older `test-utils/index.d.ts`.

0cad2799a298ff56d4358e07a32044ca2d13f03f was applied to the latest version (which the older `react-dom-tests.ts` was using) in #30748. The older version needs it, now that `strictNullChecks` is enabled.
